Class TimeComparison

  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    DateSelector.TimeComparisons
    public class TimeComparison
extends EnumeratedAttribute
    EnumeratedAttribute for time comparisons. Accepts values "before", "after", "equal".

    Ant 1.7
